#-----handy-ruler-for-slack-desc-width-------------------------------|
make_slack_desc << EOF "Python audio metadata module"
Mutagen is a Python module to handle audio metadata. It supports ASF, 
FLAC, M4A, Monkey's Audio, MP3, Musepack, Ogg Opus, Ogg FLAC, Ogg 
Speex, Ogg Theora, Ogg Vorbis, True Audio, WavPack and OptimFROG audio 
files. All versions of ID3v2 are supported, and all standard ID3v2.4 
frames are parsed. It can read Xing headers to accurately calculate 
the bitrate and length of MP3s. ID3 and APEv2 tags can be edited 
regardless of audio format. It can also manipulate Ogg streams on an 
individual packet/page level. 

EOF

